snippet.textDisplay:
I reckon if we all just roll out into this world without ever being taught any type of prejudice, or racism, or bodyshaming themed insults or bullying and we see Lizzo for the first time we all would just think how gorgeous she is.
And for those of you who thinks i'm giving backhanded compliments, i know that i'm not. If i just wrote "omg she's so gorgeous" the fatphobics would roll their eyes thinking that I must be trying so hard to be accepted into today 's "pc culture" (whatever that means). I'm just here dissecting my own thoughts, trying to bridge the opposing opinions and if they can't handle it 💁‍♀️ guess we'll just have our own little fun here.

And yeah it sucks that there needs to be a paragraph of explanation when i just want to compliment this girl. But complicated girls are the best girls
